item.title: Zayn's debut solo album lands at Number 1: "It's mind-blowing"
item.description:
Zayn's debut solo album lands at Number 1: "It's mind-blowing"

By Rob Copsey (@robcopsey) Congratulations to Zayn, who lands straight in at Number 1 on this week's Official Albums Chart with his solo debut. Mind Of Mine takes the top spot on this week's chart, finishing just over 4,000 combined sales ahead of his closest rival, Adele's 25, which is knocked down to second place.

item.title: Toy Story Moleskines Are a Convincing Reason to Switch Back to Pen and Paper
item.description:
Toy Story Moleskines Are a Convincing Reason to Switch Back to Pen and Paper

Even obsessive Evernote users might want to consider switching back to pen and paper now that Moleskine has a new line of Toy Story-themed notebooks featuring artwork from the character style guides that Pixar had created for the original film over 21 years ago.
